# W3 Module Interaction Contracts (v0.1)

## 1. Module Communication Interfaces

### BBX19 → All Modules
```json
{
  "directive": {"type": "string", "required": true},
  "priority": {"type": "enum": ["low", "medium", "high", "critical"]},
  "deadline": {"type": "timestamp"}
}Gemini → System Validation

```json
{
  "validation_request": {"type": "object", "required": true},
  "risk_level": {"type": "string"},
  "recommendation": {"type": "string"}
}
```

DeepSeek → Pattern Analysis

```json
{
  "pattern_data": {"type": "object", "required": true},
  "analysis_type": {"type": "enum": ["structure", "behavior", "anomaly"]},
  "confidence_score": {"type": "float"}
}
```

ChatGPT → Flow Generation

```json
{
  "flow_spec": {"type": "object", "required": true},
  "complexity": {"type": "enum": ["simple", "moderate", "complex"]},
  "test_cases": {"type": "array"}
}
```

Grok → Narrative Output

```json
{
  "narrative_input": {"type": "object", "required": true},
  "interpretation_level": {"type": "enum": ["summary", "detailed", "technical"]},
  "anomaly_flags": {"type": "array"}
}
```

Copilot-Gm → Orchestration

```json
{
  "orchestration_command": {"type": "string", "required": true},
  "target_modules": {"type": "array", "required": true},
  "execution_context": {"type": "object"}
}
```

2. Cross-Module Message Standards

Request-Response Pattern

```json
{
  "message_id": {"type": "uuid", "required": true},
  "source_module": {"type": "string", "required": true},
  "target_module": {"type": "string", "required": true},
  "timestamp": {"type": "timestamp", "required": true},
  "payload": {"type": "object", "required": true}
}
```

3. Error Handling Contracts

Validation Errors

```json
{
  "error_code": {"type": "string", "required": true},
  "error_message": {"type": "string", "required": true},
  "suggested_fix": {"type": "string"},
  "retry_possible": {"type": "boolean"}
}
```

4. Sync & Version Contracts

Module Sync Agreement

· All modules MUST use same contract version
· Version mismatch MUST trigger immediate sync
· Breaking changes REQUIRE 24-hour notification
